data.title: Christmas Is Jesus
data.meta_description: Your church can experience the signature style of Mike Speck in a collection focused on the Christmas season.  The message of the Gospel rings out loud and clear in Christmas Is Jesus, a  musical that echoes the true reason for our seasonal celebration -- it
